00:36:00,880 --> 00:36:03,213
Arsyeja pse u tha kjo eshte,

405
00:36:03,213 --> 00:36:05,921
se sot duhet te shohim Shri Ganeshen,

406
00:36:05,963 --> 00:36:08,255
qe eshte Nena Toke,

407
00:36:09,796 --> 00:36:11,297
qe vepron nepermjet Nenes Toke.

408
00:36:11,297 --> 00:36:16,213
Shumica e gjerave qe kemi jane prej Nenes Toke.

409
00:36:18,880 --> 00:36:21,172
Pra kete radhe duhet te shikoni Nenen Toke,

410
00:36:21,172 --> 00:36:27,796
Kundalinin dhe Shri Ganeshan, sot.

411
00:36:28,921 --> 00:36:33,130
Nena Toke ka krijuar Shri Ganeshan.

412
00:36:33,130 --> 00:36:37,755
Pra ju s'shihni asgje jashte, madje s'shihni as henen.

