445
00:39:28,963 --> 00:39:31,921
Ajo thote, "Cfare do te thote ta vesh sarin ne toke,

446
00:39:31,963 --> 00:39:33,880
cfare di ti per Gjyshen time?

447
00:39:33,921 --> 00:39:36,297
Ajo eshte Zoti i Zotave

448
00:39:36,338 --> 00:39:39,088
dhe ti ve sarin e Saj ne toke.

449
00:39:40,338 --> 00:39:46,963
Qente do te hane ty tani, " i thote, " Kij kujdes. "

450
00:39:47,005 --> 00:39:51,088
Dhe shkoi perseri vuri sarin, e puthi dhe puthi ate,

451
