548
00:48:02,213 --> 00:48:07,172
Imagjinoni, ju po jetoni ne token e Sadashiva

549
00:48:09,338 --> 00:48:13,963
ku "pikat (rruazat) e ujit dhe bora gjithashtu "

550
00:48:14,005 --> 00:48:17,172
jane si uje i distiluar, e paster, e kulluar, e bardhe.

551
00:48:20,130 --> 00:48:22,880
Ku Shri Ganesha eshte Ai

552
00:48:24,338 --> 00:48:27,796
qe lan kembet e Babait te Tij.

553
00:48:30,255 --> 00:48:35,755
Ku dliresia vete qendron si Nena juaj.

554
00:48:38,130 --> 00:48:43,338
Dhe ju duhet ta meritoni kete pozite te lakmuar.

555
00:48:46,130 --> 00:48:49,213
Sahaja Yogistet angleze duhet te jene shume te hapur.

556
00:48:50,297 --> 00:48:53,755
Krejtesisht e kunderta e Anglezeve ketu.

557
00:48:57,005 --> 00:49:02,130
Te ardhur prej tokes se Sadashiva-s krejt e kunderta.

558
00:49:02,130 --> 00:49:12,963
Arrogance e tmerrshme, arrogance kaq e tmerrshme,

559
00:49:13,005 --> 00:49:16,213
