582
00:51:45,921 --> 00:51:49,255
S'ka nevoje, ju jeni kaq te plotefuqishem, kaq te plotefuqishem,

583
00:51:49,297 --> 00:51:51,963
sa s'eshte nevoja te jeni agresive me askend.

584
00:51:52,005 --> 00:51:54,255
Pse te jeni agresive, s'keni frike nga askush.

585
00:51:54,297 --> 00:52:01,172
Eshte kaq bujare, eshte kaq e kendshme, eshte e bukur,

586
00:52:03,755 --> 00:52:11,088
gjithmone e fresket dhe e re, ende kaq sublime dhe dinjitoze.

587
00:52:16,172 --> 00:52:19,046
Kane kaluar 12 vjet qe kur kam qene ketu.

588
00:52:19,046 --> 00:52:24,213
Edhe dy vjet me shume, nevojitet pune shume intensive,

589
00:52:24,255 --> 00:52:29,755
brenda dhe jashte. Brenda duhet te punojme shume

590
00:52:29,755 --> 00:52:32,005
keto dy vjet, shume pune,

591
00:52:32,005 --> 00:52:35,005
duhet te futemi vertet ne tapasya

592
00:52:38,255 --> 00:52:42,880
te gjithe ne, qofshim burre apo grua.

593
00:52:48,338 --> 00:52:51,297
Dhe me pas do te shohim.

594
00:52:53,838 --> 00:53:01,088
Mund ta them kete, qe kemi bere nje pune te mire,

595
00:53:02,796 --> 00:53:09,921
